commit.message:
Fix indentline concealcursor command

The indent line command to remove the its concealcursor setting has changed and is now `let g:indentLine_concealcursor=""` I altered the spelling to match the new setting (as per the docs there is no longer a `noConcealCursor` command)

Fix indentline concealcursor command

The indent line command to remove the its concealcursor setting has changed and is now `let g:indentLine_concealcursor=""` I altered the spelling to match the new setting (as per the docs there is no longer a `noConcealCursor` command)

commit.message:
Improve jsonBoolean and jsonNumber highlight colors

currently it's highlighted as `Delimiter`. But there are
`Boolean` and `Number` for boolean values and numbers by default.
If there is no special reason, vim-json should use them.

Official syntax/json.vim does it.

https://github.com/vim/vim/blob/master/runtime/syntax/json.vim
Detect AWS CloudFormation templates
setlocal filetype instead of apparently troublesome setfiletype in ftdetect
added link to manual install instructions

Merge pull request #49 from nyerup/issue-48

indent: Only use func shiftwidth() if it exists

indent: Only use func shiftwidth() if it exists

shiftwidth() is not a builtin function, and my vim mojo isn't strong
enough to know where it could have come from. This change fallbacks to
using &sw instead of the shiftwidth() function, if the latter doesn't
exist.

Fixes Issue #48 in https://github.com/elzr/vim-json
